{"tid":2075250,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"桂山島上面有支那人住，送比香港＝廢除關口？","createTime":"2020-06-22T17:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:58:33.000Z","uid":143343,"like":131,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3551c5d6df6d335d079cc4377c823ce7ab6593b0","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3HkH0R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3HkH0R.jpg&h=2690ffa8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3j4K9FS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3j4K9FS.jpg&h=b624dd45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMa6Dzd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMa6Dzd.jpg&h=ef3ba4d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桂山島唔係荒島，係珠海一部分<br />\n<br />\n如果格硬填海送比香港<br />\n<br />\n我估應該唔係趕走上面既建築物同埋支那人<br />\n<br />\n而係比支那人可以係桂山島自由出入香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qjJLT8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqjJLT8D.jpg&h=98b506c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OiQFH2k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOiQFH2k.jpg&h=52fdf14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZfnbVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZfnbVM.jpg&h=cbe566c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6sr2bV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6sr2bV9.jpg&h=f73be2c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nHXT227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnHXT227.jpg&h=e4af4ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面既相黎自支那既公開桂山島遊記<br />\n<br />\n桂山島上面又有民宿又有平房，仲有學校<br />\n<br />\n擺明之後係想比支那人自出自入香港"},{"pid":"3481c78e48e5961b883c14b5dc6dc2f311398be3","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"如果比支那人自出自入就大件事<br />\n<br />\n到時唔係一日150個，隨時係一日15000個"},{"pid":"f9d0f768c51efa8cb9d53c23ae6b8ddc23bc4c2c","tid":2075250,"uid":77547,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"萬山群島+九段線都割俾香港就考慮下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819e4f7b7d790b86b6cf052f3957944140067e54","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:07:41.000Z","msg":"呢個計劃應該係廢除香港關口既第一步"},{"pid":"e4707521a3cd79e5e85dc853182cc08cbbfaec95","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"f9d0f768c51efa8cb9d53c23ae6b8ddc23bc4c2c","tid":2075250,"uid":77547,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"萬山群島+九段線都割俾香港就考慮下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:09:42.000Z","msg":"萬山群島比較好，起碼係荒島<br />\n<br />\n桂山島就唔係，會變成一個缺口"},{"pid":"af3eb9a817850f98a4be92fda3954bbe221e084c","tid":2075250,"uid":105176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"支那島 個名唔錯"},{"pid":"62d6129bbc2c07c6ed5d069e96b7c8caad3bf2fe","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"希望大家去諗下呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港已經玩完<br />\n<br />\n但守得一步得一步"},{"pid":"ef11b99a931b9451ffa1a59c4b997f52fcd50e65","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af3eb9a817850f98a4be92fda3954bbe221e084c","tid":2075250,"uid":105176,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:11:58.000Z","msg":"支那島 個名唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:15:24.000Z","msg":"支那人支那島<br />\n<br />\n想入侵香港"},{"pid":"14b0fcbf837292b422c0217e6db2eae2023e3559","tid":2075250,"uid":361247,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"62d6129bbc2c07c6ed5d069e96b7c8caad3bf2fe","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"希望大家去諗下呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港已經玩完<br />\n<br />\n但守得一步得一步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"應該會趕走桂山島居民,以澳大為例支那會趕橫琴人走起圍牆,就算唔趕佢哋都要等七年先可成新香港人。<br />\n<br />\n不過我都係建議台灣容許香港人係東沙建特區。"},{"pid":"208d5120f811a8404b5c425eb2dea1359e06635b","tid":2075250,"uid":361247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9d0f768c51efa8cb9d53c23ae6b8ddc23bc4c2c","tid":2075250,"uid":77547,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:07:33.000Z","msg":"萬山群島+九段線都割俾香港就考慮下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"咁香港土地問題可以解決"},{"pid":"cdc4076bd40009742fcf99f57319236d7296ba0f","tid":2075250,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T17:19:59.000Z","msg":"橫琴2.0，搞得成香港就仆街了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引渡全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"bedc72af29dbee02cbe993bbb06d72a65c557e25","tid":2075250,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b0fcbf837292